KEY INSIGHTS:

70% of employees experience stress every single day
80% have no private space at work to decompress
90% would use a bookable wellness pod at their workplace
Personalization and privacy were the top two priorities for any stress-relief tool
60% prefer sessions of 5—10 minutes, making short pod sessions ideal
Music and guided breathing were the most preferred relaxation methods
